<plot>The film is a documentary portrait of Jorgen Leth, structured around the poem The Perfect Human. Norway, September 2004. The young filmmaker meets one of his idols - the famous Danish film director Jorgen Leth. They decided to make a movie together. The film has been shot for a day in the hotel's lift, which was Schindler's lift.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?047461</url></doc>
